<DOCNO> LA081694-0092 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 070288 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 16, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
