EXECUTIVE SUITE: COMPANY TOWN; ZACH HOROWITZ NAMED COO AT MCA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Zach Horowitz has been named chief operating officer of MCA Entertainment 
Group, where he will focus on international operations, new technology and 
day-to-day management of the company under Chairman Al Teller. Horowitz was 
previously executive vice president at MCA. 
</P>
<P>
 * Ruth L. Otte, president and chief operating officer of Discovery Networks, 
is leaving the cable TV company to become president of Knowledge Adventure 
Inc., a fast-growing multimedia educational software company in La Crescenta. 
The company's former chief executive, Rod Turner, resigned in February. Otte, 
45, was at Discovery for eight years. Otte's successor is programming executive 
Gregory B. Moyer. 
</P>
<P>
 * Brandon Bates has been named director of development at dick clark 
productions. Bates previously worked for comedian Martin Lawrence's You Go Boy 
Productions. 
</P>
<P>
 * Michael Forman has joined Brillstein/Grey Communications as director of 
television. Brillstein/Grey also announced a development deal with Paul Simms, 
who worked on "The Larry Sanders Show." 
</P>
<P>
 * Continuing the shake-up in its public relations department, ABC has named 
Mark R. Johnson vice president of network communications. Johnson, a longtime 
Washington press secretary and Capitol Hill aide, will oversee the network's 
West Coast operations. 
</P>
<P>
 * Annabelle Stevens has been named president of Warren Cowan & Associates. 
</P>
<P>
 * Richard S. Reisberg is the new president and chief operating officer of 
Trimark Holdings Inc. 
</P>
<P>
 * Mimi Wunderlich is director of sales promotions and publicity for Republic 
Pictures Entertainment. 
</P>
<P>
 * Stephen K. Peeples and David Dorn have been named co-directors of the Rhino 
Entertainment media relations department. 
</P>
<P>
 The company has also appointed executives to its Kid Rhino division. Torrie 
Dorrell is the director of Kid Rhino, Robin Frederick is director of 
A&R/Production, and Robin Davids is marketing coordinator. 
</P>
