 The Barretts were volunteer clinic escorts who were taking Britton to the 
Ladies Center clinic in Pensacola when they were shot July 29. 
</P>
<P>
 In state court, Hill faces two counts of first-degree murder and one each of 
attempted murder and shooting into an occupied vehicle. 
