<P>
 Armenian independence -- An article in Monday's editions on the visit of 
Armenian President Levon Ter-Petrossian incorrectly stated that the country 
became independent in 1991 for the first time in 600 years. Armenia was an 
independent republic from 1918 to 1920, when it was seized by the Soviet Union. 
